{
  "sections": [
    {
      "endAnimation": {
        "type": "fade"
      },
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The Bard.",
          "duration": 1.23,
          "animation": {
            "type": "scrollRight"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "pause",
          "duration": 0.81
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "History remembers these jovial beings as master of song and story.",
          "duration": 5.66,
          "animation": {
            "type": "scrollRight"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "pause",
          "duration": 1.39
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "endAnimation": {
        "type": "fade"
      },
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Those who bask in their tales may learn the triumph of a hero’s adventure or the rule of a tyrannical king and his subjects.",
          "duration": 10.06,
          "animation": {
            "type": "scrollRight"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "pause",
          "duration": 0.59
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "endAnimation": {
        "type": "fade"
      },
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Their ballads pass swiftly through village streets to bring hope and cheer to the locals.",
          "duration": 6.17,
          "animation": {
            "type": "scrollRight"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "pause",
          "duration": 0.48
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Countless are renowned throughout the many kingdoms.",
          "duration": 3.04,
          "animation": {
            "type": "scrollRight"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "pause",
          "duration": 0.39
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "endAnimation": {
        "type": "fade"
      },
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "It is difficult to be in the presence of one and resist the urge to smile or laugh.",
          "duration": 5.5,
          "animation": {
            "type": "scrollRight"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "pause",
          "duration": 0.9
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "At least this is how the life of a bard once was in the Kingdom of Briarwood...",
          "duration": 5.52,
          "animation": {
            "type": "scrollRight"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "pause",
          "duration": 0.65
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "endAnimation": {
        "type": "fade"
      },
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Only whispers remain of the bards and their good-natured will.",
          "duration": 5.19,
          "animation": {
            "type": "scrollRight"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "pause",
          "duration": 0.52
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "endAnimation": {
        "type": "fade"
      },
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Some individuals speculate they have gone to kingdoms that are more rich in coin.",
          "duration": 4.6,
          "animation": {
            "type": "scrollRight"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "pause",
          "duration": 0.62
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Others believe it to be the result of an infuriated king’s axe caused by a previous Bard’s mocking limerick.",
          "duration": 7.3,
          "animation": {
            "type": "scrollRight"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "pause",
          "duration": 0.25
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "endAnimation": {
        "type": "fade"
      },
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Few know what actually caused the disappearance of these melody weavers….and only one bard remains in Briarwood.",
          "duration": 8,
          "animation": {
            "type": "scrollRight"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "pause",
          "duration": 0.81
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "endAnimation": {
        "type": "fade"
      },
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Raised since birth by his grandfather, Bradley Trebleton was instructed in the ways of the bard.",
          "duration": 6.33,
          "animation": {
            "type": "scrollRight"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "pause",
          "duration": 0.51
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "endAnimation": {
        "type": "fade"
      },
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Learning how to charm people with a beautiful piece played by his flute.",
          "duration": 3.78,
          "animation": {
            "type": "scrollRight"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "pause",
          "duration": 0.53
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Enthralling others with the colorful tales passed down from his grandfather.",
          "duration": 4.5,
          "animation": {
            "type": "scrollRight"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "pause",
          "duration": 0.56
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "endAnimation": {
        "type": "fade"
      },
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Bradley was infatuated with the Bard lifestyle",
          "duration": 3.47,
          "animation": {
            "type": "scrollRight"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "pause",
          "duration": 0.25
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "but never being on an adventure himself felt his stories lacked experience.",
          "duration": 4.81,
          "animation": {
            "type": "scrollRight"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "pause",
          "duration": 0.47
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "endAnimation": {
        "type": "fade"
      },
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "After his grandfather passed away several months ago,",
          "duration": 3.2,
          "animation": {
            "type": "scrollRight"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "pause",
          "duration": 0.44
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Bradley began spending most of his time at the local pub.",
          "duration": 3.62,
          "animation": {
            "type": "scrollRight"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "pause",
          "duration": 0.92
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The",
          "duration": 0.43,
          "animation": {
            "type": "scrollRight"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "pause",
          "duration": 1.34
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Trouser’s Snake.",
          "duration": 1.28,
          "animation": {
            "type": "scrollRight"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "pause",
          "duration": 0.94
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "endAnimation": {
        "type": "fade"
      },
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "And like most nights,",
          "duration": 1.67,
          "animation": {
            "type": "scrollRight"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Bradley finds himself in a drunken slumber next to the chamber pot.",
          "duration": 5.02,
          "animation": {
            "type": "scrollRight"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "pause",
          "duration": 0.76
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "endAnimation": {
        "type": "fade"
      },
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "But tonight is not like most nights",
          "duration": 2.37,
          "animation": {
            "type": "scrollRight"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "pause",
          "duration": 0.25
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "and Bradley will soon discover a place thought to be forgotten...",
          "duration": 4.42,
          "animation": {
            "type": "scrollRight"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "pause",
          "duration": 1
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
